author: Adela Suliman and Dartunorro Clark and Ken Dilanian and Courtney Kube and Alex Shi and Eric Baculinao
title: Laboratory in Wuhan breaks silence to deny claims that coronvarius originated there
description: "There is no way this virus came from us,' said Yuan Zhiming, a vice director of the Wuhan Institute of Virology.
content:
A laboratory in the Chinese city of Wuhan has broken its silence to deny accusations that the novel coronavirus originated there.
